---
---

<section class="bg-stone-50 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
 
    
    <!-- STRIDE Acronym -->
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
          What is <span class="text-primary">Stride</span>?
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 font-semibold px-2">
          Smart Travel Routes & Insights for Discovery and Experience
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
        
        <!-- S - Smart -->
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md sm:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-primary">S</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Smart</h4>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">
                Because the system isn't just a map; it's an intelligent local guide powered by AI.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- T - Travel -->
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md sm:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-secondary">T</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Travel</h4>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">
                Captures movement, commuting, exploring—whether it's jeepneys, shops, cafés, or routes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- R - Routes -->
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md sm:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-primary">R</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Routes</h4>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">
                The heart of the app: finding paths, directions, and nearest terminals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- I - Insights -->
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md sm:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-secondary">I</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Insights</h4>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">
                The system doesn't just tell where, it provides helpful context, options, and local knowledge.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- D - Discovery -->
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md sm:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-primary">D</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Discovery</h4>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">
                For uncovering new local spots—restaurants, shops, landmarks—beyond the usual tourist stops.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- E - Experience -->
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md sm:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 sm:gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-secondary">E</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Experience</h4>
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">
                The whole journey becomes smoother, richer, and more enjoyable.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>
